    <item>
      <title>韩国和日本寻求强化货币互换协议的方法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/south-korea-japan-to-seek-ways-to-reinforce-currency-swap-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本和韩国同意寻求加强货币互换协议的途径，以解决日元和韩元持续走弱导致进口成本上升并加剧通胀压力的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/south-korea-japan-to-seek-ways-to-reinforce-currency-swap-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 07:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾副总统杜特尔特称其父亲和兄弟正在考虑参选参议院：ABS-CBN</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/philippine-vp-duterte-says-dad-brothers-eyeing-senate-abs-cbn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 ABS-CBN 报道，菲律宾副总统萨拉·杜特尔特周二表示，菲律宾前总统罗德里戈·杜特尔特和他的两个儿子将参加 2025 年中期选举参议员竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/philippine-vp-duterte-says-dad-brothers-eyeing-senate-abs-cbn</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 07:44:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者称英国需要结束“什么都不建”的风气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/uk-needs-to-end-build-absolutely-nothing-ethos-insurer-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国基础设施项目的一位主要投资者表示，该国“不在我家后院”的文化正在阻碍生产力和区域经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/uk-needs-to-end-build-absolutely-nothing-ethos-insurer-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 07:40:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>彭博法国民调：极右翼勒庞领先优势扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/bloomberg-french-poll-of-polls-far-right-le-pen-s-lead-widens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的民意调查显示，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼国民联盟在周日法国提前立法选举第一轮投票前扩大了领先优势，而其竞争对手则势头减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/bloomberg-french-poll-of-polls-far-right-le-pen-s-lead-widens</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 07:36:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克里姆林宫助手称印度总理莫迪将访问俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/indian-premier-modi-to-visit-russia-kremlin-aide-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宫外交政策助理尤里·乌沙科夫称，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪预计将自乌克兰战争爆发以来首次访问俄罗斯，具体日期将稍后公布。]]></description>
