      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 07:30:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚警察在税收表决前封锁议会大楼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/kenyan-police-barricade-parliament-precinct-before-vote-on-taxes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚立法者就引发广泛抗议的新税进行投票，警方在议会周围设置了路障，企业关闭了首都的办事处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/kenyan-police-barricade-parliament-precinct-before-vote-on-taxes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 06:08:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本母子在中国城市遭刀袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/japanese-mother-child-attacked-with-knife-in-city-near-shanghai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名日本妇女和她的孩子在中国上海附近的一个城市遭到持刀袭击，这让这个暴力事件相对罕见的国家出现了一系列持刀伤人事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/japanese-mother-child-attacked-with-knife-in-city-near-shanghai</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 01:41:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
